Type: Package
Package: PedSV
Title: Helper R functions for studies of germline SVs in pediatric cancers
Version: 0.0.2
Author: Ryan Collins <Ryan_Collins@dfci.harvard.edu>
Maintainer: Ryan Collins <Ryan_Collins@dfci.harvard.edu>
Description: This package contains various utility functions used in a
    DFCI study of germline structural variants in pediatric cancers.
